// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2025-0217 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: e78c769d-25b5-585c-b9ab-23664f7b13ac

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *ubuntu:14.04* OR ImageFileName = *ubuntu:16.04* OR ImageFileName = *ubuntu:16.04-ESM* OR ImageFileName = *ubuntu:17.04* OR ImageFileName = *ubuntu:17.10*)
